
BIOS:
F000  4C 30 F0 JMP @retry
F003  4C 3C F0 JMP _PUTCHAR
F006  4C 48 F0 JMP ACK_IRQ
F009  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F00C  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F00F  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F012  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F015  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F018  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F01B  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F01E  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F021  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F024  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F027  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F02A  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY
F02D  4C 53 F0 JMP EMPTY

@retry:
F030  AD 00 D0 LDA $D000
F033  F0 FB    BEQ @retry
F035  9C 00 D0 STZ $D000
F038  29 7F    AND #$7F
F03A  18       CLC
F03B  60       RTS

_PUTCHAR:
F03C  48       PHA

@busy:
F03D  AD 01 D0 LDA $D001
F040  D0 FB    BNE @busy
F042  68       PLA
F043  8D 01 D0 STA $D001
F046  18       CLC
F047  60       RTS

ACK_IRQ:
F048  48       PHA
F049  9C 0C E0 STZ $E00C

@wait_ack:
F04C  AD 0F E0 LDA $E00F
F04F  D0 FB    BNE @wait_ack
F051  68       PLA
F052  60       RTS

EMPTY:
F053  00       BRK
F054  EA       NOP
